sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Cliente/Aplicación
    participant OSB as CreditManagementRouter_PS
    participant DVM as RegionalParameters DVM
    participant DataWH as DataWareHouseHN
    participant Rules as RulesManagement
    participant BLAZE as BLAZE Advisor
    participant ErrorSvc as GetErrorMessages_BS
    participant LogSvc as SetLogInfoService_BS

    Note over Client, LogSvc: Flujo Honduras (HN01) - CreditManagementRouter_PS

    Client->>OSB: REST/SOAP Request
    Note right of Client: Endpoint: v1.0/credit-management<br/>Operation: getConsolidatedCustomerRisk<br/>SourceBank: HN01<br/>DestinationBank: HN01

    OSB->>OSB: CommonParams Stage
    Note right of OSB: Asignar variables:<br/>codigoServicio: '3'<br/>language: ES<br/>sourceBank: HN01<br/>destinationBank: HN01<br/>serviceName: GetConsolidatedCustomerRisk_PS

    OSB->>DVM: Validar Servicio Regional
    Note right of DVM: Lookup: ServiceName=GetConsolidatedCustomerRisk_PS<br/>Name=SourceBank.HN01.DestinationBank.HN01

    alt Región No Válida
        DVM->>OSB: Value != 'Active'
        OSB->>Client: Error MW-0003: INVALID REGION REQUEST
    end

    DVM->>OSB: Value = 'Active'
    DVM->>OSB: Location = DataWareHouseHN/RequestorServices/ProxyServices/v1.0/

    OSB->>OSB: Branch por Operación
    Note right of OSB: Determinar operación:<br/>getConsolidatedCustomerRisk

    OSB->>OSB: GetConsolidatedRiskPP Pipeline
    Note right of OSB: Transformar request usando:<br/>Tx_GetConsolidatedCustomerRisk_To_consulta_ONBASE_V2.xqy

    OSB->>DataWH: Dynamic Route
    Note right of DataWH: Endpoint: DataWareHouseHN_BS<br/>Operation: consulta_ONBASE_V2<br/>Parámetros:<br/>- PV_CEDULA: 0801199012345<br/>- PV_NIT: 08011990123456789<br/>- PV_NOMBRE: JUAN<br/>- PV_APELLIDO: PEREZ<br/>- PV_FECHA_NACIMIENTO: 1990-01-08

    alt Error en DataWareHouse
        DataWH->>OSB: Error Response
        OSB->>ErrorSvc: GetErrorMessages Request
        Note right of ErrorSvc: Parámetros:<br/>- codigoErrorSistema: DB_ERROR<br/>- codigoServicio: '3'<br/>- codigoSistema: '1'<br/>- codigoLenguaje: ES

        ErrorSvc->>OSB: Error Mapping Response
        OSB->>OSB: Transform Error
        Note right of OSB: Tx_ErrorMap_To_ErrorInfo.xqy<br/>Mapear a estructura estándar

        OSB->>LogSvc: Log Error Request
        Note right of LogSvc: Tx_Msg_To_SetLogInfo.xqy<br/>- codigoAplicacion: 1<br/>- codigoServicio: '3'<br/>- estado: 'Error'<br/>- uuid: generated

        OSB->>Client: Error Response
        Note left of Client: HTTP Code: 500<br/>ErrorInfo con código mapeado
    end

    DataWH->>OSB: Success Response
    Note left of DataWH: PV_CODIGO_ERROR: SUCCESS<br/>PV_SCORE_EXTERNO: 750<br/>PV_CALIFICACION: EXCELLENT<br/>PV_NIVEL_RIESGO: LOW<br/>PV_SALARIO: 25000.00<br/>PV_EDAD: 34

    OSB->>OSB: Transform Response
    Note right of OSB: Tx_consulta_ONBASE_V2_To_GetConsolidatedCustomerRiskResponse.xqy<br/>Mapear campos:<br/>PV_SCORE_EXTERNO → ExternalScore<br/>PV_CALIFICACION → Qualification<br/>PV_NIVEL_RIESGO → RiskLevel

    OSB->>OSB: FlujoSalida Stage
    Note right of OSB: Verificar ErrorInfo en response<br/>Si hay error, mapear HTTP code

    OSB->>Client: Success Response
    Note left of Client: StatusInfo:<br/>- GlobalId: UUID<br/>- SuccessIndicator: SUCCESS<br/>- Messages: Consulta exitosa<br/><br/>GetConsolidatedCustomerRisk:<br/>- ExternalScore: 750<br/>- Qualification: EXCELLENT<br/>- RiskLevel: LOW

    Note over Client, LogSvc: Flujo Alternativo - getCreditOffers

    Client->>OSB: getCreditOffers Request
    Note right of Client: Operation: getCreditOffers<br/>CustomerInfo con datos del cliente<br/>ProductNature: PERSONAL_LOAN

    OSB->>OSB: CommonParams Stage
    Note right of OSB: codigoServicio: '8'<br/>serviceName: GetCreditOffers_PS

    OSB->>DVM: Validar Servicio Regional
    DVM->>OSB: Location = RulesManagement/RequestorServices/ProxyServices/v1.0/

    OSB->>OSB: GetCustomerOffers Pipeline
    Note right of OSB: Transformar request usando:<br/>Tx_GetCreditOffers_To_BLAZE.xqy

    OSB->>Rules: Dynamic Route
    Note right of Rules: Endpoint: RulesManagement_BS<br/>Datos del cliente para evaluación

    Rules->>BLAZE: Execute Rules
    Note right of BLAZE: Evaluar:<br/>- customerId: 0801199012345<br/>- salary: 25000.00<br/>- age: 34<br/>- externalScore: 750<br/>- productNature: PERSONAL_LOAN<br/>- region: HN01

    BLAZE->>Rules: Rules Result
    Note left of BLAZE: Ofertas calculadas:<br/>- ProductCode: PERSONAL_LOAN<br/>- MaxAmount: 500000.00<br/>- Rate: 12.50<br/>- Terms: 12,24,36 meses

    Rules->>OSB: BLAZE Response

    OSB->>OSB: Transform Response
    Note right of OSB: Tx_BLAZE_To_GetCreditOffersResponse.xqy<br/>Mapear ofertas a estructura OSB

    OSB->>Client: getCreditOffers Response
    Note left of Client: GetCreditOffers:<br/>- InternalScore: 750<br/>- InternalRiskLevel: LOW<br/>- ResolutionOffers con términos<br/>- MaxOffer: 500000.00<br/>- Rate: 12.50%

    Note over Client, LogSvc: Transformaciones Clave HN01:
    Note over Client, LogSvc: 1. Request → consulta_ONBASE_V2 (DataWareHouse)
    Note over Client, LogSvc: 2. consulta_ONBASE_V2 → GetConsolidatedCustomerRiskResponse
    Note over Client, LogSvc: 3. Request → BLAZE format (RulesManagement)
    Note over Client, LogSvc: 4. BLAZE → GetCreditOffersResponse
    Note over Client, LogSvc: 5. Error mapping con códigos HTTP
    Note over Client, LogSvc: 6. Logging centralizado de transacciones